In the oil holding study, after the impregnation process, the BC pellicles were wiped carefully with filter paper, placed on an analytical balance (accurate to 0.0001 g), weighed and then centrifuged 2,000 RPM for 5 min x 5. Every 5 min, BC sample was weighed. EO holding capacity values were calculated using the formula (1):1\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
